      "span_text": "As noted in the Introduction section, Fridgen and co-workers  in their IRMPD/computation study found that the Li + cation in the BLi + (H 2 O) n = 1,2 (B = uracil, thymine) complexes is coordinated to the O4 atom, and the first two water molecules of these complexes are attached to the lithium cation."
